Herald Squire		KEY:Cavalier Archetype ~ Herald Squire								CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.CavalierArchetype.CavalierTactician.CavaliersCharge						PRECLASS:1,Cavalier=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Cavalier Archetype ~ Herald Squire],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.CavalierInitiativeDeed,TYPE.CavaliersDodgeDeed]						DESC:The herald squire is the eyes and ears of a traveling knight, often arriving ahead of her liege to bring word of his arrival, find lodgings, and get the lay of the land.																																																																																				ABILITY:Cavalier Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Herald Squire ~ Introduction|PRECLASS:1,Cavalier=1	ABILITY:Cavalier Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Herald Squire ~ Fleet of Foot|PRECLASS:1,Cavalier=2	ABILITY:Cavalier Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Herald Squire ~ Transcend Language|PRECLASS:1,Cavalier=3																				COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.21	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Cavalier	FACT:Cavalier_Archetype_OrderAbility2|True	FACT:Cavalier_CF_OrderAbility2|True
Introduction		KEY:Herald Squire ~ Introduction									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.CavalierClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.CavalierTactician																																								DESC:Whenever a herald squire tries to influence a creature's attitude with the Diplomacy skill for the first time, she may roll her Diplomacy check twice and take the best result. In addition, any improvement of a creature's attitude toward the herald squire also applies to her knight.																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.21
Fleet of Foot		KEY:Herald Squire ~ Fleet of Foot									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.CavalierClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																											DESC:At 2nd level, a herald squire gains fast movement, as the barbarian class feature of the same name. Whenever she makes long overland journeys alone or with only her mount, the distance a herald squire can travel each day increases by 20%%. This ability replaces the 2nd-level order ability.																																																																																																																			BONUS:MOVEADD|TYPE=Walk|10|PREVARLT:ENCUMBERANCE,2,var("COUNT[EQTYPE.ARMOR.EQUIPPED.IS.HEAVY]"),1			SOURCEPAGE:p.21
Transcend Language	KEY:Herald Squire ~ Transcend Language								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.CavalierClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.SpellLike.CavaliersCharge																																									DESC:Three times per day, a herald squire can cast tongues on herself, using her herald squire level as her caster level. The effects of this ability last for a number of rounds equal to her herald squire level.																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.21

