# Fighter Archetype
# ==============================

Weapon Bearer Squire	KEY:Fighter Archetype ~ Weapon Bearer Squire							CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.FighterArchetype.FighterBonusFeat1.FighterBonusFeat2.FighterArmorTraining1			PRECLASS:1,Fighter=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Fighter Archetype ~ Weapon Bearer Squire],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.FighterBonusFeat1,TYPE.FighterBonusFeat2,TYPE.FighterArmorTraining1]	DESC:With myriad weapons, armor, and useful gear always on hand, the weapon bearer squire ensures her knight is equipped for any task.																																																																																											ABILITY:Fighter Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Bearer Squire ~ Weapon Rack|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=1	ABILITY:Fighter Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Bearer Squire ~ Swift Sharpening|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=2	ABILITY:Fighter Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Bearer Squire ~ Combat Repairs|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=3																			COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.21	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Fighter
Weapon Rack			KEY:Weapon Bearer Squire ~ Weapon Rack								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.FighterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.FighterBonusFeat1																																								DESC:Once per round, a knight can retrieve an item carried by his weapon bearer squire as a move action that does not provoke attacks of opportunity. In addition, a weapon bearer squire can pick up items dropped by her knight as an immediate action without provoking attacks of opportunity. The knight and the weapon bearer squire must be adjacent to each other and must both be able to move and communicate to use these abilities. This ability replaces the 1st-level fighter bonus combat feat.																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.21
Swift Sharpening		KEY:Weapon Bearer Squire ~ Swift Sharpening							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.FighterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.FighterBonusFeat2																																								DESC:A weapon bearers quire can quickly hone her lord's weapons to make them more effective in combat. As a full-round action, a weapon bearer squire can use a whetstone to sharpen a weapon she is holding, granting whoever wields the weapon a +1 circumstance bonus on his next attack roll with that weapon. In addition, she can apply a weapon blanch (UE p.105) to a weapon she is holding as a standard action, instead of a full-round action. This ability replaces the 2nd-level fighter bonus combat feat.																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.21
Combat Repairs		KEY:Weapon Bearer Squire ~ Combat Repairs								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.FighterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.FighterArmorTraining1																																							DESC:A weapon bearer squire can ensure her liege never goes unarmed, even if his weapon has all but shattered. As a full-round action, a weapon bearer squire can make rapid repairs to a weapon she is holding and is proficient with by succeeding at a DC 20 Craft (weapons) check. The item does not regain any hit points, but loses the broken condition for a number of rounds equal to the weapon bearer squire's class level.																																																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.21

# ==============================
# Gunslinger Archetype
# ==============================

Gunner Squire		KEY:Gunslinger Archetype ~ Gunner Squire								CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.GunslingerArchetype.GunslingersDodgeDeed.GunslingerInitiativeDeed.GunslingerNimble	PRECLASS:1,Gunslinger=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Gunslinger Archetype ~ Gunner Squire],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.GunslingerInitiativeDeed,TYPE.GunslingersDodgeDeed,TYPE.GunslingerNimble]	DESC:Prepared to reload or repair her lord's firearms at a moment's notice, the gunner squire is an indispensable aid for knights skilled in the use of pistols and rifles.																																																																																					ABILITY:Gunslinger Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Gunner Squire ~ Spotter|PRECLASS:1,Gunslinger=1	ABILITY:Gunslinger Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Gunner Squire ~ Side Arm|PRECLASS:1,Gunslinger=3	ABILITY:Gunslinger Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Gunner Squire ~ Safe Handling|PRECLASS:1,Gunslinger=2																				COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.20	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Gunslinger
Spotter			KEY:Gunner Squire ~ Spotter				SORTKEY:Class_Gunslinger_Deed_LVL01	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.GunslingerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.DeedsLVL1.DeedHasCost																																						DESC:As a standard action, a gunner squire can spend 1 grit point to pinpoint a target within her line of sight and inform her knightly liege of the target's exact location. During the knight's next turn, if he makes a ranged attack against the pinpointed target and would take a penalty on his attack roll due to range, he may reduce this penalty by an amount equal to his gunner squire's Wisdom modifier (to a minimum penalty of 0). The gunner squire must be adjacent to her liege and able to communicate to use this deed, though a knight may move away from the gunner squire during his turn and still gain the benefits of this deed.																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.20
Side Arm			KEY:Gunner Squire ~ Side Arm				SORTKEY:Class_Gunslinger_Deed_LVL03	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.GunslingerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.DeedsLVL3.DeedHasCost																																						DESC:As a full-round action, a gunner squire can spend 1 grit point to reload a one-handed or two-handed firearm she is holding. If the firearm has multiple barrels, she can reload a number of barrels per round equal to her Dexterity modifier (minimum 1). A gunner squire equipped with alchemical cartridges can use this deed to reload multiple firearms at once, dividing the number of barrels she's able to reload among the firearms she is carrying however she wishes, even if this would mean stowing and retrieving multiple firearms from her equipment with one action. Abilities, deeds, and feats that decrease reloading time (such as Rapid Reload) do not improve this deed.																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.21
Safe Handling		KEY:Gunner Squire ~ Safe Handling									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.GunslingerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.GunslingerNimble																																								DESC:As a full-round action, a gunner s quire can temporarily ensure the safety of a firearm she is holding, reducing its misfire chance by 1 (to a minimum of 0) on the next attack roll made with that firearm. This reduction does not stack with itself. This reduction occurs after any increases are calculated for firing with the broken condition, or for any other effect that might increase the misfire value of a firearm.																																																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.21

