Combat Healer Squire	KEY:Paladin Archetype ~ Combat Healer Squire							CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.PaladinArchetype.PaladinDetectEvil.PaladinDivineGrace.PaladinDivineHealth			PRECLASS:1,Paladin=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Paladin Archetype ~ Combat Healer Squire],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.PaladinDetectEvil,TYPE.PaladinDivineGrace,TYPE.PaladinDivineHealth]		DESC:Always ready with bandages and potions, the combat healer squire keeps her knight on his feet against all odds, and always has just the right remedy on hand.																																																																																						ABILITY:Paladin Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Combat Healer Squire ~ Careful Healer|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=1	ABILITY:Paladin Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Combat Healer Squire ~ Dress Wounds|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=2	ABILITY:Paladin Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Combat Healer Squire ~ Swift Healer|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=3																		COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.20	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Paladin
Careful Healer		KEY:Combat Healer Squire ~ Careful Healer								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.PaladinClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.PaladinDetectEvil																																								DESC:A combat healer squire provokes no attacks of opportunity when she uses the Heal skill to stabilize a creature or treat poison. In addition, when she administers long-term care with the Heal skill, she can restore a total number of additional hit points equal to her character level, divided as she wishes among those she is tending.																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.20
Dress Wounds		KEY:Combat Healer Squire ~ Dress Wounds								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.PaladinClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.PaladinDivineGrace																																								DESC:A combat healer squire can hastily dress a deadly wound for her knight, temporary alleviating his suffering. This ability acts in all ways like using the Heal skill to treat deadly wounds, except the combat healer squire only needs to take a full-round action to use this ability. The hit points healed are temporary, and only last 10 minutes, but they are not lost first like temporary hit points. A combat healer squire can only use this ability on her knight, not other creatures. A knight cannot benefit from this ability more than once per day, and cannot be treated for deadly wounds with the Heal skill within 24 hours of being subjected to this ability.																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.20
Swift Healer		KEY:Combat Healer Squire ~ Swift Healer								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.PaladinClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.PaladinDivineHealth																																								DESC:A combat healer squire can use the Heal skill to perform first aid or treat poison as a swift action.																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.20
